title: Milburn, Nebraska
text:
Milburn is an <a href="unincorporated%20community">unincorporated community</a> in <a href="Custer%20County%2C%20Nebraska">Custer County</a>, <a href="Nebraska">Nebraska</a>, United States.
History.
A post office at Milburn was established in 1887 by James Milburn, and named for him.
